#. type: Title =
#: upstream/_guides/security-basic-authentication-howto.adoc:2
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Enable Basic authentication"
msgstr "启用基本认证"

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_guides/security-basic-authentication-howto.adoc:7
#, fuzzy
msgid "Enable xref:security-basic-authentication-concept.adoc[Basic authentication] for your Quarkus project and allow users to authenticate with a username and password."
msgstr "为你的Quarkus项目启用基本认证，允许用户用用户名和密码进行认证。"

#. type: Title ==
#: upstream/_guides/security-basic-authentication-howto.adoc:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "Prerequisites"
msgstr "先决条件"

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_guides/security-basic-authentication-howto.adoc:11
#, fuzzy
msgid "You have installed at least one extension that provides an `IdentityProvider` based on username and password, such as xref:security-jdbc.adoc[Elytron JDBC]."
msgstr "你至少安装了一个基于用户名和密码提供 `IdentityProvider` 的扩展，如 link:security-jdbc.html[Elytron JDBC] 。"

#. type: Title ==
#: upstream/_guides/security-basic-authentication-howto.adoc:12
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure"
msgstr "程序"

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_guides/security-basic-authentication-howto.adoc:15
#, fuzzy
msgid "Enable Basic authentication by setting the value of `quarkus.http.auth.basic` property to `true`."
msgstr "通过将 `quarkus.http.auth.basic` 属性的值设置为 `true` ，启用基本认证。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: upstream/_guides/security-basic-authentication-howto.adoc:19
#, no-wrap
msgid "quarkus.http.auth.basic=true\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_guides/security-basic-authentication-howto.adoc:22
#, fuzzy
msgid "An easy way to configure the required user credentials for Basic authentication to work is to configure the user name, secret, and roles directly in the `application.properties` file."
msgstr "配置Basic认证所需的用户凭证的一个简单方法是直接在 `application.properties` 文件中配置用户名、密码和角色。"

#. type: Block title
#: upstream/_guides/security-basic-authentication-howto.adoc:23
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Example of Basic authentication properties"
msgstr "基本认证属性的例子"

#. type: delimited block -
#: upstream/_guides/security-basic-authentication-howto.adoc:33
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"quarkus.http.auth.basic=true\n"
"quarkus.security.users.embedded.plain-text=true\n"
"quarkus.security.users.embedded.users.alice=alice\n"
"quarkus.security.users.embedded.users.bob=bob\n"
"quarkus.security.users.embedded.roles.alice=admin\n"
"quarkus.security.users.embedded.roles.bob=user\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_guides/security-basic-authentication-howto.adoc:36
#, fuzzy
msgid "In this configuration the credentials for users `alice` and `bob` are configured: `alice` has a password `alice` and an `admin` role, `bob` has a password `bob` and a `user` role."
msgstr "在这个配置中，配置了用户 `alice` 和 `bob` 的凭证： `alice` 有一个密码 `alice` 和一个 `admin` 角色， `bob` 有一个密码 `bob` 和一个 `user` 角色。"

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_guides/security-basic-authentication-howto.adoc:38
msgid "For more information, see xref:security-testing.adoc#configuring-user-information[Configuring User Information] in the \"Security Testing\" guide."
msgstr ""

